33:/// TRACE_MATRIX FC1-N7 + §15 (selective shielding bounded-context-window)
34:/// — TB-G G2P.1 charter §1 Module G2P. Default cap on rows rendered.
35:/// Keeps prompt context bounded; the agent can still verify any WorkTx
36:/// visible in `=== Current Chain ===` directly — this block is a curated
