41:/// TRACE_MATRIX FC1-N7 + §17 reporting standard — TB-G G2P.2 charter §1
42:/// Module G2P atom G2P.2. Aggregate + per-axis peer-verification
43:/// coverage view derived from L4 walk.
44:///
45:/// `solver_agents` = agents who submitted ≥1 accepted WorkTx on this
46:/// chain. `non_solver_verifications` counts accepted VerifyTxs whose
47:/// `verifier_agent ∉ solver_agents` — the architect §8.2 ship gate
48:/// signal ("at least one non-solver VerifyTx on another agent's
49:/// WorkTx").
